---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="소개" description="블로그와 저자에 대한 소개">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
      <h1>소개</h1>
      
      <p class="lead">
        안녕하세요! 개발을 사랑하는 엔지니어입니다.
        이 블로그에서는 제가 배우고 경험한 것들을 공유합니다.
      </p>

      <h2>관심 분야</h2>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>웹 개발</strong>: React, Vue, Astro 등 모던 프레임워크</li>
        <li><strong>성능 최적화</strong>: Core Web Vitals, 번들 최적화</li>
        <li><strong>개발자 경험</strong>: 도구와 워크플로우 개선</li>
        <li><strong>오픈소스</strong>: 커뮤니티 기여와 협업</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>기술 스택</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">React</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Next.js</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Astro</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Tailwind CSS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Backend</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Node.js</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Python</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-sm">Redis</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>이 블로그에 대해</h2>
      
      <p>
        이 블로그는 <strong>Astro</strong>와 <strong>TypeScript</strong>로 구축되었습니다.
        정적 사이트 생성(SSG)을 통해 빠른 로딩 속도와 뛰어난 SEO를 제공합니다.
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>프레임워크: Astro v4</li>
        <li>스타일링: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui</li>
        <li>콘텐츠: MDX + Content Collections</li>
        <li>배포: GitHub Pages</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>연락처</h2>
      
      <p>
        프로젝트 협업이나 문의사항이 있으시면 언제든 연락주세요!
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4 not-prose">
        <a
          href="https://github.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
        >
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        
        <a
          href="mailto:contact@example.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground"
        >
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          Email
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>